# Rupture {#sec-rupture}


::: {.cell}

:::


Not all volunteers work until the end of their contract. In fact, 22.9% of volunteers have a "rupture", i.e. terminate the contract early (@fig-rupture-overview). There are various motives for ending one's contract early (@fig-rupture-motive). Not all of them are necessarily bad, e.g. "Embauche en CDD d'au moins 6 mois ou CDI", and some are outside of the influence of the volunteers, e.g. "Fin de validité du Titre de Séjour". 


